1
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:55,000
"Lost To You"

2
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,700
(Episode 8)

3
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,799
When the storm hits,

4
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:01,699
some choose to cower,

5
00:01:01,700 --> 00:01:06,199
some choose to light
themselves up as torches,

6
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:08,499
but true courage

7
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:10,499
is when the whole world
turns its back on you,

8
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:12,500
and you're still holding each other's hands.

9
00:01:18,208 --> 00:01:19,916
Isn't this the Jinx's sister?

10
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:22,625
I heard your brother ruined Lin Xia's hand.

11
00:01:23,666 --> 00:01:24,767
What nonsense are you talking about?

12
00:01:24,791 --> 00:01:25,831
My brother was saving her!

13
00:01:25,916 --> 00:01:26,934
Her injury was an accident!

14
00:01:26,958 --> 00:01:27,666
An accident?

15
00:01:27,833 --> 00:01:28,916
He's just a jinx.

16
00:01:29,083 --> 00:01:30,166
And a homosexual.

17
00:01:30,291 --> 00:01:31,916
Your whole family is trash.

18
00:01:32,541 --> 00:01:34,166
And you still want to be a star?

19
00:01:34,416 --> 00:01:35,083
How embarrassing.

20
00:01:35,291 --> 00:01:36,333
Stop talking nonsense!

21
00:01:37,375 --> 00:01:38,416
The Jinx family,

22
00:01:38,541 --> 00:01:39,541
get out of our school!

23
00:01:39,875 --> 00:01:40,583
Get out of our class!

24
00:01:40,625 --> 00:01:41,166
Get out!

25
00:01:41,333 --> 00:01:42,375
Get out of our school!

26
00:01:42,576 --> 00:01:44,096
- You dare hit me?
- Get out of our class!

27
00:01:44,458 --> 00:01:45,458
You guys...

28
00:01:45,541 --> 00:01:46,541
Just you wait!

29
00:01:46,583 --> 00:01:48,143
I'm going to tell my brother right now!

30
00:01:56,833 --> 00:01:58,433
The jinx and the gay guy are still here.

31
00:01:58,583 --> 00:01:59,375
They have some nerve.

32
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:00,958
Exactly. Just get lost.

33
00:02:01,041 --> 00:02:02,309
Don't ruin our school's reputation.

34
00:02:02,333 --> 00:02:02,833
Zhan Wang,

35
00:02:02,916 --> 00:02:03,750
your brother likes men.

36
00:02:03,791 --> 00:02:04,875
Do you like men too?

37
00:02:05,666 --> 00:02:06,958
You're with the jinx every day.

38
00:02:07,125 --> 00:02:07,916
Are you guys hooking up?

39
00:02:07,916 --> 00:02:08,541
Yeah, right?

40
00:02:08,708 --> 00:02:09,708
Are you guys sick?

41
00:02:09,833 --> 00:02:10,833
What are you looking at?

42
00:02:11,125 --> 00:02:12,434
Outsiders aren't welcome in our class.

43
00:02:12,458 --> 00:02:13,458
Everyone, get out!

44
00:02:15,333 --> 00:02:16,333
Lin Xia...

45
00:02:16,833 --> 00:02:18,000
It's all because of Lin Xia.

46
00:02:18,375 --> 00:02:19,434
Don't you have your own classrooms?

47
00:02:19,458 --> 00:02:20,458
Go back!

48
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:23,750
Go, go, go.

49
00:02:23,791 --> 00:02:24,875
Who wants to watch anyway?

50
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,166
Jinx. Jinx.

51
00:02:31,458 --> 00:02:32,601
Why is it that the people around me

52
00:02:32,625 --> 00:02:34,000
always get hurt because of me?

53
00:02:35,833 --> 00:02:36,416
It's raining.

54
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:37,750
Let's go together.

55
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:39,791
Come on.

56
00:02:44,791 --> 00:02:45,791
Xiang Bei.

57
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Xiang Bei.

58
00:02:51,375 --> 00:02:52,495
I heard you're transferring.

59
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,458
Xiao Bei's athletic
recruitment fell through.

60
00:02:55,833 --> 00:02:57,583
I plan to send him abroad for high school.

61
00:02:57,958 --> 00:02:58,958
He'll study abroad.

62
00:02:59,708 --> 00:03:01,166
You're Xiao Bei's friend?

63
00:03:02,791 --> 00:03:03,791
Just classmates.

64
00:03:04,875 --> 00:03:05,250
Mom.

65
00:03:05,708 --> 00:03:06,708
Let's go.

66
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
Xiang Bei.

67
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:17,250
I'm sorry.

68
00:03:23,083 --> 00:03:23,666
Lin Xia.

69
00:03:23,916 --> 00:03:25,517
How do you still have
the nerve to lie here?

70
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:26,741
Now everyone in town is saying

71
00:03:26,791 --> 00:03:28,166
my brother ruined your hand.

72
00:03:28,333 --> 00:03:29,916
But he clearly did it to save you!

73
00:03:30,166 --> 00:03:31,625
How can you be so heartless?

74
00:03:31,791 --> 00:03:32,916
Stop playing the victim!

75
00:03:33,041 --> 00:03:34,041
Are you family?

76
00:03:34,375 --> 00:03:34,916
Keep it down.

77
00:03:34,986 --> 00:03:35,986
You're in a hospital.

78
00:03:36,708 --> 00:03:37,708
I'm her enemy.

79
00:03:38,208 --> 00:03:39,208
Don't cause trouble.

80
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:43,666
Bear with the pain.

81
00:03:44,541 --> 00:03:45,601
The recovery is going well,

82
00:03:45,625 --> 00:03:47,705
but absolutely do not put
any pressure on this hand.

83
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:51,541
What's with the fight between sisters?

84
00:03:52,583 --> 00:03:53,583
Take better care of her.

85
00:03:58,250 --> 00:03:59,450
Did you come here to scold me?

86
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,500
Go ahead.

87
00:04:02,125 --> 00:04:03,458
I just wanted to ask

88
00:04:03,666 --> 00:04:05,666
if you spread those videos on purpose

89
00:04:06,166 --> 00:04:07,166
to get my brother blamed.

90
00:04:08,041 --> 00:04:09,041
Yes.

91
00:04:09,833 --> 00:04:10,541
I just couldn't stand

92
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:12,333
how inseparable he and Zhan Wang were.

93
00:04:12,541 --> 00:04:14,208
I hurt my own hand on purpose,

94
00:04:14,625 --> 00:04:15,791
hired someone to film it,

95
00:04:15,875 --> 00:04:16,750
and framed your brother on purpose.

96
00:04:16,875 --> 00:04:17,916
How could you?

97
00:04:22,958 --> 00:04:24,038
You actually believed that?

98
00:04:24,791 --> 00:04:25,791
You're pretty cute.

99
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:27,875
I love painting.

100
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,625
I would never sacrifice my own hand

101
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:31,916
over some relationship drama.

102
00:04:32,333 --> 00:04:33,613
As for the videos you mentioned,

103
00:04:33,958 --> 00:04:35,250
I don't know who spread them.

104
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:37,541
The scene was too chaotic that day.

105
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:40,333
But

106
00:04:41,833 --> 00:04:43,153
I do owe your brother an apology.

107
00:04:45,333 --> 00:04:46,500
He really did save me.

108
00:04:49,041 --> 00:04:50,333
I guess I just have bad luck.

109
00:04:52,416 --> 00:04:53,875
I was destined to get this injury.

110
00:05:11,083 --> 00:05:12,083
Here.

111
00:05:12,291 --> 00:05:13,571
You look like you're struggling.

112
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:14,750
Thanks.

113
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:23,833
Zhan Wang and I...

114
00:05:25,666 --> 00:05:26,666
We talked.

115
00:05:28,333 --> 00:05:29,416
Last night.

116
00:05:37,375 --> 00:05:38,375
Is my hand...

117
00:05:38,416 --> 00:05:39,416
Your hand is fine.

118
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,750
The doctor told me.

119
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:44,650
We've known each other for so long.

120
00:05:44,958 --> 00:05:45,958
I'll take care of you.

121
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:47,250
Don't worry.

122
00:05:56,041 --> 00:05:57,041
But

123
00:05:58,458 --> 00:06:00,178
there's something I need to tell you today.

124
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:04,708
I like Xu Yuan.

125
00:06:11,875 --> 00:06:12,875
You...

126
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,125
Do you know what...

127
00:06:14,125 --> 00:06:15,125
I know.

128
00:06:15,416 --> 00:06:16,776
I won't be like my second brother.

129
00:06:17,958 --> 00:06:19,278
If I like Xu Yuan, I'll admit it.

130
00:06:21,708 --> 00:06:23,458
And I will love him openly

131
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,250
and protect him.

132
00:06:25,958 --> 00:06:27,518
I won't let him get hurt because of me.

133
00:06:29,833 --> 00:06:30,833
Lin Xia,

134
00:06:33,666 --> 00:06:34,666
my brother's path...

135
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,330
I won't walk down it again.

136
00:06:37,958 --> 00:06:38,958
Your brother

137
00:06:39,791 --> 00:06:40,833
is a very good person.

138
00:06:43,041 --> 00:06:44,166
Zhan Wang's taste

139
00:06:45,541 --> 00:06:46,000
is pretty good.

140
00:06:46,333 --> 00:06:47,333
Of course it is.

141
00:06:51,625 --> 00:06:52,666
Actually,

142
00:06:53,791 --> 00:06:54,833
I have a brother too.

143
00:06:56,125 --> 00:06:58,166
He used to open bottle
caps for me all the time.

144
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:01,708
His hands were big

145
00:07:02,416 --> 00:07:03,416
and strong.

146
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:05,145
They were meant for holding a scalpel.

147
00:07:07,125 --> 00:07:08,791
But he never found me to be a nuisance.

148
00:07:11,458 --> 00:07:13,083
What they said before...

149
00:07:13,583 --> 00:07:14,583
is it true?

150
00:07:15,125 --> 00:07:17,875
Your brother and Zhan Xu...

151
00:07:23,041 --> 00:07:24,541
Do things like that really happen...?

152
00:07:30,958 --> 00:07:33,416
Don't worry too much about it.

153
00:07:33,791 --> 00:07:35,458
Our brothers made their own choices.

154
00:07:35,708 --> 00:07:37,625
Why should we, as sisters, interfere?

155
00:07:37,916 --> 00:07:38,916
But

156
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:40,208
you didn't have to get so angry

157
00:07:40,333 --> 00:07:41,791
at Zhan Xu in the school clinic.

158
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:43,666
Last time in the clinic,

159
00:07:43,958 --> 00:07:45,718
after you gave Zhan
Xu a piece of your mind,

160
00:07:45,875 --> 00:07:47,750
he was suspended because of it.

161
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,250
My brother

162
00:07:50,583 --> 00:07:51,583
is dead.

163
00:07:59,833 --> 00:08:00,833
I'm sorry.

164
00:08:03,541 --> 00:08:04,916
I... I didn't know.

165
00:08:12,125 --> 00:08:13,125
Look at this.

166
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:19,625
It's Zhan Xu

167
00:08:20,125 --> 00:08:21,125
With my brother.

168
00:08:23,041 --> 00:08:24,281
I painted this three years ago.

169
00:08:26,250 --> 00:08:27,458
When I was painting him,

170
00:08:28,875 --> 00:08:29,875
my brother said

171
00:08:31,125 --> 00:08:33,166
this was his happiest moment.

172
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,000
Back then,

173
00:08:36,868 --> 00:08:38,868
my brother ran away from home with Zhan Xu.

174
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,750
But

175
00:08:43,083 --> 00:08:44,625
in the end, he died on the mountain.

176
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,250
That's why I can't help but hate Zhan Xu.

177
00:08:51,125 --> 00:08:52,708
So when I saw him that day,

178
00:08:52,791 --> 00:08:53,791
I acted too impulsively.

179
00:08:54,416 --> 00:08:55,416
It's also my fault

180
00:08:56,583 --> 00:08:58,023
for dragging your brother into this.

181
00:09:00,416 --> 00:09:01,416
Lin Xia,

182
00:09:02,875 --> 00:09:03,875
I don't blame you.

183
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,000
Okay.

184
00:09:08,230 --> 00:09:10,323
["Leave"]

185
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:16,625
Mom.

186
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:19,458
You're back.

187
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:20,208
It's nothing.

188
00:09:20,208 --> 00:09:21,208
Who did this?

189
00:09:21,958 --> 00:09:23,398
A few people came by this afternoon.

190
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:25,940
They said some really nasty things.

191
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,416
It's fine. I'll just clean it up.

192
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:29,750
It's fine, really.

193
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,750
Mom,

194
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:35,041
leave it.

195
00:09:35,083 --> 00:09:36,083
Go back and rest.

196
00:09:36,416 --> 00:09:37,642
It's fine. Don't get your hands dirty.

197
00:09:37,666 --> 00:09:38,666
Let me do it.

198
00:09:39,541 --> 00:09:40,541
Go back inside.

199
00:09:55,875 --> 00:09:56,875
What happened?

200
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:58,250
Let me help.

201
00:09:58,875 --> 00:09:59,875
Mind your own business.

202
00:10:00,583 --> 00:10:01,583
Xu Yuan!

203
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,500
Just leave.

204
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,630
Do you care about what
those people are saying?

205
00:10:10,166 --> 00:10:11,206
Let's talk somewhere else.

206
00:10:20,375 --> 00:10:21,415
What on earth do you want?

207
00:10:23,416 --> 00:10:24,416
Nothing.

208
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:26,688
I just want you to stay away from me.

209
00:10:27,541 --> 00:10:28,581
Go back to your big villa.

210
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:29,995
Stop causing trouble for me.

211
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:32,833
If it weren't for you and your brother,

212
00:10:34,375 --> 00:10:36,208
my family wouldn't be in this mess.

213
00:10:36,708 --> 00:10:37,788
What are you talking about?

214
00:10:39,534 --> 00:10:40,534
Am I wrong?

215
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,666
If it weren't for you guys,

216
00:10:43,708 --> 00:10:45,668
those rumors wouldn't
have gotten so out of hand.

217
00:10:46,416 --> 00:10:48,416
Now my mom can't even
run her noodle shop anymore.

218
00:10:48,875 --> 00:10:49,875
Are you happy now?

219
00:10:51,166 --> 00:10:52,166
Xu Yuan.

220
00:10:53,416 --> 00:10:54,750
What on earth are you saying?

221
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:56,666
I've had enough.

222
00:10:58,416 --> 00:11:00,056
I'm sick of you clinging to me every day.

223
00:11:00,125 --> 00:11:02,059
I'm sick of people whispering
and pointing fingers.

224
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:04,873
I'm sick of my mom and me being dragged
into the mess you and your brother made.

225
00:11:13,208 --> 00:11:14,208
Go find someone else.

226
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:16,750
Stop bothering me.

227
00:11:19,583 --> 00:11:20,583
Master Zhan,

228
00:11:21,333 --> 00:11:22,773
I'm just a nobody from a small town.

229
00:11:23,416 --> 00:11:24,776
I can't handle this kind of drama.

230
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:30,000
And I don't want to have

231
00:11:30,083 --> 00:11:32,243
this kind of disgusting
relationship with you anymore.

232
00:11:32,583 --> 00:11:33,583
Just leave.

233
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:36,125
Xu Yuan,

234
00:11:37,291 --> 00:11:38,575
is it because I'm gay

235
00:11:40,125 --> 00:11:41,125
that you're saying this?

236
00:11:41,666 --> 00:11:42,666
Is that it?

237
00:11:43,583 --> 00:11:45,083
You can't accept that I like guys?

238
00:11:46,541 --> 00:11:47,861
You can't accept that I like you?

239
00:11:48,875 --> 00:11:50,235
That's why you're pushing me away?

240
00:11:51,416 --> 00:11:52,416
Is that it?

241
00:11:53,250 --> 00:11:54,250
Fine.

242
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,500
I get it.

243
00:11:57,458 --> 00:11:58,458
Xu Yuan,

244
00:11:59,291 --> 00:12:00,291
long time no see.

245
00:12:00,833 --> 00:12:01,833
Xiang Bei.

246
00:12:02,541 --> 00:12:03,541
I'm back.

247
00:12:03,875 --> 00:12:04,875
It seems

248
00:12:05,166 --> 00:12:06,246
I still came back too late.

249
00:12:08,458 --> 00:12:09,458
Let me walk you back.

250
00:12:34,875 --> 00:12:35,875
Brother.

251
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,500
Xiao Wang.

252
00:12:39,791 --> 00:12:40,375
What are you doing here?

253
00:12:40,583 --> 00:12:42,892
Xu Yuan's mom is having some
trouble with her noodle shop.

254
00:12:42,916 --> 00:12:44,517
Someone is forcing her to
sign a demolition agreement.

255
00:12:44,541 --> 00:12:46,476
They're playing dirty. Can
you do anything about it?

256
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:47,500
I heard about it.

257
00:12:48,083 --> 00:12:49,642
They aren't part of the government's plan.

258
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:51,546
It's an illegal operation
by a private company.

259
00:12:51,833 --> 00:12:53,017
I have a friend who's a lawyer

260
00:12:53,041 --> 00:12:54,641
who specializes in these kinds of cases.

261
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,240
Have Xu Yuan's mom contact him.

262
00:13:02,708 --> 00:13:04,125
The contract, documents,

263
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,740
and even the threats they made—

264
00:13:06,166 --> 00:13:07,166
they'll all be useful.

265
00:13:07,458 --> 00:13:08,458
Thanks.

266
00:13:08,833 --> 00:13:09,833
So,

267
00:13:10,708 --> 00:13:11,708
what about you?

268
00:13:12,083 --> 00:13:13,083
You're not

269
00:13:14,291 --> 00:13:15,291
leaving again, are you?

270
00:13:22,083 --> 00:13:23,083
I've decided to stay.

271
00:13:24,916 --> 00:13:26,676
In the past, when
things like this happened,

272
00:13:26,875 --> 00:13:27,875
my first instinct

273
00:13:28,583 --> 00:13:29,583
was always to run away.

274
00:13:30,708 --> 00:13:31,708
I thought leaving

275
00:13:32,541 --> 00:13:33,541
was best for everyone.

276
00:13:34,541 --> 00:13:36,181
I thought of it as a way to protect them.

277
00:13:37,208 --> 00:13:38,208
But now,

278
00:13:39,708 --> 00:13:40,708
I won't do that anymore.

279
00:13:41,875 --> 00:13:42,875
Because of...

280
00:13:44,583 --> 00:13:45,583
Bian Ye?

281
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,250
Yes,

282
00:13:49,541 --> 00:13:50,541
but not entirely.

283
00:13:51,458 --> 00:13:52,978
Hong Town indeed has a lot of trouble—

284
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:55,000
deep-rooted prejudices

285
00:13:55,875 --> 00:13:56,875
and hurtful rumors.

286
00:13:59,166 --> 00:14:00,166
But

287
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:03,850
there are also people I want to protect,

288
00:14:05,041 --> 00:14:06,833
and a life I want to start over,

289
00:14:07,625 --> 00:14:08,625
along with my work.

290
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:11,750
Leaving might temporarily avoid the storm,

291
00:14:11,875 --> 00:14:13,475
but it doesn't solve the problem at all,

292
00:14:13,958 --> 00:14:15,718
nor does it protect
the people I care about.

293
00:14:16,416 --> 00:14:17,416
It took me a long time

294
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:18,750
to realize this.

295
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,000
Brother,

296
00:14:23,291 --> 00:14:24,708
Bian Ye might face some trouble

297
00:14:25,583 --> 00:14:26,703
because of this controversy.

298
00:14:28,791 --> 00:14:30,083
I'll have a good talk with him.

299
00:14:31,666 --> 00:14:32,786
He has his own path to walk.

300
00:14:34,041 --> 00:14:35,333
I will respect his choice.

301
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,500
So slow.

302
00:14:45,291 --> 00:14:46,411
Isn't that Senior Xiang Bei?

303
00:14:46,581 --> 00:14:47,388
Holy shit.

304
00:14:47,666 --> 00:14:48,666
It really is him!

305
00:14:48,958 --> 00:14:50,041
He can even ride a bike.

306
00:14:50,250 --> 00:14:51,267
Looks like he's mostly recovered.

307
00:14:51,291 --> 00:14:52,125
That's amazing.

308
00:14:52,291 --> 00:14:53,411
He actually made a recovery.

309
00:14:53,458 --> 00:14:54,458
Senior,

310
00:14:54,583 --> 00:14:55,416
are you coming back to the swim team?

311
00:14:55,541 --> 00:14:55,958
Of course.

312
00:14:56,041 --> 00:14:57,681
How could I ever stay away from the pool?

313
00:15:00,041 --> 00:15:01,161
I have to go. See you later.

314
00:15:01,416 --> 00:15:01,791
Okay.

315
00:15:01,875 --> 00:15:02,458
Take care!

316
00:15:02,791 --> 00:15:03,791
Morning, Xu Yuan.

317
00:15:07,416 --> 00:15:09,333
We didn't get to catch
up properly yesterday.

318
00:15:09,916 --> 00:15:10,916
During lunch break,

319
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:12,450
I'll wait for you at the pool.

320
00:15:15,208 --> 00:15:16,000
I'm off then.

321
00:15:16,208 --> 00:15:17,208
See you at noon.

322
00:15:25,958 --> 00:15:26,958
Does it still hurt?

323
00:15:27,541 --> 00:15:28,581
It healed a long time ago.

324
00:15:29,375 --> 00:15:30,541
Don't look at me like that.

325
00:15:31,375 --> 00:15:32,375
Seriously, Xu Yuan,

326
00:15:32,625 --> 00:15:33,625
I'm really fine now.

327
00:15:34,291 --> 00:15:35,291
Then,

328
00:15:36,583 --> 00:15:37,625
can you still swim?

329
00:15:39,708 --> 00:15:40,708
Yeah, I can.

330
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,000
I can run, jump,

331
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:43,666
ride a bike, and swim.

332
00:15:44,208 --> 00:15:45,208
It's just that...

333
00:15:45,541 --> 00:15:46,583
I can't compete

334
00:15:46,708 --> 00:15:47,708
as an athlete anymore.

335
00:15:48,375 --> 00:15:50,291
The bones

336
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:51,416
and ligaments here

337
00:15:51,833 --> 00:15:53,553
have signed a permanent truce with my body.

338
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:55,125
I'm sorry.

339
00:15:55,375 --> 00:15:56,000
I... I...

340
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:57,250
It's okay.

341
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:58,750
Don't say that.

342
00:15:59,291 --> 00:16:01,083
Look at me, aren't I doing great now?

343
00:16:02,083 --> 00:16:03,976
The old coach asked me to
come back as an assistant coach,

344
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,520
and I agreed without a second thought.

345
00:16:06,708 --> 00:16:07,708
Xu Yuan,

346
00:16:08,375 --> 00:16:09,495
I didn't come back this time

347
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:11,416
to make you feel guilty,

348
00:16:11,916 --> 00:16:13,333
nor did I want to reclaim anything.

349
00:16:15,041 --> 00:16:16,041
I just felt

350
00:16:16,875 --> 00:16:17,875
there were things

351
00:16:18,541 --> 00:16:19,861
we didn't say properly back then,

352
00:16:20,833 --> 00:16:22,753
and I owed you an
explanation at the very least.

353
00:16:23,416 --> 00:16:24,416
I understand.

354
00:16:24,916 --> 00:16:25,916
After all,

355
00:16:26,375 --> 00:16:27,495
after such a major accident,

356
00:16:28,250 --> 00:16:29,583
anyone would want to cut ties.

357
00:16:29,875 --> 00:16:30,875
That's not true.

358
00:16:31,333 --> 00:16:33,813
Saying we shouldn't contact
each other was just said in anger.

359
00:16:34,708 --> 00:16:36,458
I sent you so many messages,

360
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:38,666
but you never replied.

361
00:16:38,916 --> 00:16:41,250
I was in closed rehabilitation,
and my mom took my phone away.

362
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,290
By the time I got it back when I was better

363
00:16:45,291 --> 00:16:46,541
and saw the messages you sent,

364
00:16:46,916 --> 00:16:48,396
your number had already been disconnected.

365
00:16:50,791 --> 00:16:52,391
I didn't have anyone important to reach,

366
00:16:53,416 --> 00:16:54,892
so I stopped using a phone after that.

367
00:16:54,916 --> 00:16:55,916
That's why I came back—

368
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,666
to explain everything to you.

369
00:16:58,333 --> 00:17:00,041
I never wanted to cut ties with you.

370
00:17:03,291 --> 00:17:04,291
Hello, Coach Xiang.

371
00:17:07,875 --> 00:17:08,916
Isn't that the Jinx?

372
00:17:09,083 --> 00:17:10,142
Why is he with the assistant coach?

373
00:17:10,166 --> 00:17:10,833
Don't you know?

374
00:17:11,041 --> 00:17:12,583
Xiang got injured because of him.

375
00:17:13,708 --> 00:17:14,788
Lunch break is almost over.

376
00:17:15,458 --> 00:17:16,458
I'm going back to class.

377
00:17:16,583 --> 00:17:17,583
Okay.

378
00:17:22,458 --> 00:17:23,458
Xu Yuan.

379
00:17:24,083 --> 00:17:25,083
If you're willing,

380
00:17:25,666 --> 00:17:27,426
come help me as a
manager for the swim team.

381
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:28,916
I really need some help.

382
00:17:29,041 --> 00:17:30,041
Would you?

383
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,500
I'll think about it.

384
00:17:37,583 --> 00:17:38,783
I have a new phone number now.

385
00:18:02,396 --> 00:18:05,496
[Ninety nine [!] unread
messages from Xiang Bei]

386
00:18:10,875 --> 00:18:11,875
Just got my phone back.

387
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:13,691
My mom took it away for two months.

388
00:18:13,833 --> 00:18:15,125
Surgery and rehab.

389
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:17,068
She was afraid I'd get distracted.

390
00:18:17,458 --> 00:18:18,458
I saw your messages.

391
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,750
All of them.

392
00:18:20,166 --> 00:18:21,246
I didn't know how to reply.

393
00:18:21,916 --> 00:18:22,916
It's not your fault.

394
00:18:23,208 --> 00:18:24,208
It never was.

395
00:18:24,916 --> 00:18:25,916
Xu Yuan,

396
00:18:26,041 --> 00:18:27,881
you're not the one who
should be saying sorry.

397
00:18:28,583 --> 00:18:29,983
I was able to get out of bed today.

398
00:18:30,416 --> 00:18:31,416
Don't worry anymore.

399
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:34,200
The therapist said I'm
recovering faster than expected.

400
00:18:34,625 --> 00:18:36,625
She asked if I have a high pain tolerance.

401
00:18:37,166 --> 00:18:38,166
I didn't answer.

402
00:18:38,625 --> 00:18:40,065
Today, I managed to walk ten meters.

403
00:18:40,541 --> 00:18:41,541
It hurts,

404
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,750
but it's progress.

405
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:44,666
The sunset here is gray.

406
00:18:45,041 --> 00:18:46,321
It doesn't compare to Hong Town.

407
00:18:46,916 --> 00:18:48,375
Xu Yuan, don't be afraid.

408
00:18:48,916 --> 00:18:49,958
And don't say sorry anymore.

409
00:18:50,666 --> 00:18:51,666
The new school is huge,

410
00:18:52,375 --> 00:18:54,015
but it doesn't have the pool I'm used to.

411
00:18:54,958 --> 00:18:56,838
I saw a video of the
sunset in Hong Town today.

412
00:18:57,291 --> 00:18:58,331
It's still as red as ever.

413
00:18:58,666 --> 00:18:59,666
Did you see the sunset?

414
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:02,101
I've started preparing for
the college entrance exam.

415
00:19:02,125 --> 00:19:03,165
We might not talk as much.

416
00:19:03,541 --> 00:19:04,621
Take good care of yourself.

417
00:19:31,083 --> 00:19:32,083
It's Xu Yuan.

418
00:19:33,875 --> 00:19:36,500
When should I come find you at the pool?

419
00:20:04,875 --> 00:20:05,458
From now on,

420
00:20:05,666 --> 00:20:07,586
if anyone dares to mention
the word 'gay' again,

421
00:20:07,916 --> 00:20:09,958
Bian Ye will just knock
them out with one punch.

422
00:20:12,166 --> 00:20:14,000
But Zhan Wang and my brother...

423
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:16,333
it's like they've swapped souls lately.

424
00:20:17,041 --> 00:20:19,541
Zhan Wang buries himself
in studying in class every day,

425
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,708
while my brother skips class all the time.

426
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:23,700
I watched them for a long time

427
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,950
before I finally figured out
what my brother was up to.

428
00:20:26,166 --> 00:20:28,541
He's working as an administrator
for Xiang Bei's swim team.

429
00:20:28,708 --> 00:20:29,708
Ready.

430
00:20:31,125 --> 00:20:32,125
Keep going, keep going!

431
00:20:34,916 --> 00:20:35,333
How is it?

432
00:20:35,625 --> 00:20:36,825
Are you settling into the job?

433
00:20:37,958 --> 00:20:39,318
This is how I check it off, right?

434
00:20:39,458 --> 00:20:39,916
Yeah.

435
00:20:40,083 --> 00:20:41,083
Do you like the job?

436
00:20:44,041 --> 00:20:45,561
Alright, warm up over there, everyone.

437
00:20:45,708 --> 00:20:46,908
Get ready to jump in. Warm up.

438
00:20:46,958 --> 00:20:48,278
Chest stretches, chest stretches.

439
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:50,500
That guy, Zhan Wang...

440
00:20:51,041 --> 00:20:52,208
isn't he even going to try?

441
00:20:53,541 --> 00:20:56,083
Maybe he's just completely disheartened.

442
00:21:01,791 --> 00:21:03,083
Here, sister, this is for you.

443
00:21:05,541 --> 00:21:06,781
Thank you for coming to see me.

444
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:09,708
It's what a little angel is supposed to do.

445
00:21:10,111 --> 00:21:13,194
Sister, can you still draw with your hand?

446
00:21:14,041 --> 00:21:15,041
Of course I can.

447
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,000
Don't believe me?

448
00:21:17,833 --> 00:21:18,333
Close your eyes.

449
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,500
I'll give you a surprise.

450
00:21:29,541 --> 00:21:30,541
Look.

451
00:21:34,041 --> 00:21:35,041
Your hand is injured,

452
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:36,351
and you can still draw so beautifully.

453
00:21:36,375 --> 00:21:36,875
Sister,

454
00:21:37,291 --> 00:21:38,791
you're a naturally gifted artist.

455
00:21:57,916 --> 00:21:58,916
Will this really work?

456
00:22:00,041 --> 00:22:01,375
They are not to be messed with.

457
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:02,875
Don't worry, Auntie.

458
00:22:03,541 --> 00:22:04,916
This is a professional lawyer.

459
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:07,125
For illegal demolitions like theirs,

460
00:22:07,250 --> 00:22:08,650
a lawsuit is guaranteed to succeed.

461
00:22:09,041 --> 00:22:09,541
Just remember,

462
00:22:09,916 --> 00:22:11,636
keep the recordings of them causing trouble

463
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:12,750
and that fake contract.

464
00:22:13,166 --> 00:22:14,934
Keep them safe and hand
them over to the lawyer.

465
00:22:14,958 --> 00:22:16,476
I've prepared a lot of
other things here too.

466
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:17,500
It will definitely work.

467
00:22:19,416 --> 00:22:20,875
Wang-wang, thank you.

468
00:22:21,458 --> 00:22:23,666
You've done so much for this family.

469
00:22:24,416 --> 00:22:24,791
Auntie,

470
00:22:25,166 --> 00:22:26,166
this is my home too.

471
00:22:28,208 --> 00:22:29,208
Then I'll go tell Xu Yuan

472
00:22:29,291 --> 00:22:30,291
the good news too.

473
00:22:30,833 --> 00:22:31,833
Okay.

474
00:22:31,916 --> 00:22:32,333
Goodbye.

475
00:22:32,708 --> 00:22:33,708
Take care.

476
00:22:47,750 --> 00:22:48,750
Thank you, Xu Yuan.

477
00:22:49,250 --> 00:22:51,570
You being willing to help me
as an admin for the swim team

478
00:22:51,791 --> 00:22:52,791
is a huge help.

479
00:22:53,541 --> 00:22:54,581
It's the least I could do.

480
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:56,550
It's great that you're
back on the swim team.

481
00:22:57,958 --> 00:22:58,958
Doing a bit more work

482
00:23:00,125 --> 00:23:02,205
is my way of making up
for all these years of guilt.

483
00:23:03,625 --> 00:23:05,265
During the two years my mom took me away,

484
00:23:06,791 --> 00:23:07,958
I tried a lot of things.

485
00:23:08,916 --> 00:23:09,916
But I realized

486
00:23:10,416 --> 00:23:11,416
what I love most

487
00:23:12,125 --> 00:23:13,125
is still swimming.

488
00:23:14,166 --> 00:23:15,166
Xu Yuan,

489
00:23:15,416 --> 00:23:17,500
it seems once I love something,

490
00:23:18,916 --> 00:23:19,916
I can't let it go.

491
00:23:25,541 --> 00:23:26,541
You seem...

492
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,360
not to be afraid of water anymore.

493
00:23:30,750 --> 00:23:32,030
I had to overcome it eventually.

494
00:23:32,875 --> 00:23:33,875
Did someone help you?

495
00:23:34,708 --> 00:23:35,708
Yes.

496
00:23:36,916 --> 00:23:37,916
Zhan Wang?

497
00:23:44,291 --> 00:23:45,291
I like you.

498
00:23:46,708 --> 00:23:47,708
Xu Yuan.

499
00:24:27,791 --> 00:24:29,291
Xu Yuan, your mom's noodle shop...

500
00:24:37,708 --> 00:24:38,708
Zhan Wang.

501
00:24:39,041 --> 00:24:40,041
Zhan Wang.

502
00:24:40,166 --> 00:24:41,166
Zhan Wang.

503
00:25:03,375 --> 00:25:04,375
Xu Yuan.

504
00:25:05,333 --> 00:25:06,333
Xu Yuan.

505
00:25:06,875 --> 00:25:07,875
Xu Yuan.

506
00:25:09,875 --> 00:25:10,875
Xu Yuan.

507
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:18,625
I like you.

508
00:25:19,279 --> 00:25:20,119
Fuck!

509
00:25:27,583 --> 00:25:28,583
Stop drinking.

510
00:25:29,208 --> 00:25:30,392
Xu Yuan is looking everywhere for you.

511
00:25:30,416 --> 00:25:32,496
He's practically turning the
whole town upside down.

512
00:25:36,791 --> 00:25:38,250
What's it to him?

513
00:25:39,458 --> 00:25:41,541
Let him go find his gentle, caring,

514
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:44,583
and swimming-expert old flame.

515
00:25:45,250 --> 00:25:46,730
Aren't they doing just fine together?

516
00:25:47,226 --> 00:25:47,846
Fuck!

517
00:25:47,958 --> 00:25:49,250
Stop being so sarcastic with me.

518
00:25:49,541 --> 00:25:50,767
If you're angry, don't take it out on me.

519
00:25:50,791 --> 00:25:52,231
If you've got the guts, let's fight.

520
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,750
Bring it on!

521
00:25:59,916 --> 00:26:01,184
Do you think this is easy for me?

522
00:26:01,208 --> 00:26:02,392
When I was called a bastard as a kid,

523
00:26:02,416 --> 00:26:03,416
who could I talk to?

524
00:26:03,583 --> 00:26:05,000
Now I finally met Zhan Xu,

525
00:26:05,083 --> 00:26:06,583
only to be judged by those idiots.

526
00:26:06,958 --> 00:26:08,041
My brother protected you.

527
00:26:08,333 --> 00:26:09,500
My brother protected you.

528
00:26:10,083 --> 00:26:11,163
My brother didn't run away.

529
00:26:11,416 --> 00:26:12,416
But what about me?

530
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:14,460
I don't even have the
right to stand by his side.

531
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:15,750
Then go tell him that!

532
00:26:15,916 --> 00:26:16,916
Tell him you like him!

533
00:26:17,083 --> 00:26:18,041
Instead of hiding here like a coward,

534
00:26:18,083 --> 00:26:19,083
waiting to die.

535
00:26:19,583 --> 00:26:20,583
I am waiting to die.

536
00:26:21,125 --> 00:26:22,208
I am waiting to die.

537
00:26:22,541 --> 00:26:24,208
Before I die, I like him!

538
00:26:24,458 --> 00:26:25,458
Is that so wrong?

539
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,291
I'm not afraid of anything.

540
00:26:33,166 --> 00:26:34,291
Why did he choose him?

541
00:26:35,291 --> 00:26:36,375
Why did he lie to me?

542
00:26:36,708 --> 00:26:38,250
He kept saying he doesn't like men.

543
00:26:38,458 --> 00:26:39,041
He doesn't like men.

544
00:26:39,291 --> 00:26:41,000
Then why did he choose him?

545
00:26:41,250 --> 00:26:42,250
Why did he lie to me?

546
00:26:42,416 --> 00:26:43,416
Why?

547
00:26:44,250 --> 00:26:45,291
Calm down!

548
00:26:54,625 --> 00:26:55,625
Zhan Wang.

549
00:26:57,833 --> 00:26:58,833
Zhan Wang.

550
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:02,791
I told Xiang Bei.

551
00:27:04,666 --> 00:27:05,666
I don't like him.

552
00:27:09,208 --> 00:27:10,208
Right.

553
00:27:11,375 --> 00:27:13,458
It's because you never
liked men in the first place.

554
00:27:14,916 --> 00:27:15,916
It's me.

555
00:27:17,333 --> 00:27:18,541
I'm the one who's crazy.

556
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:25,750
Zhan Wang.

557
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:29,500
Zhan Wang.

558
00:27:32,041 --> 00:27:33,041
I like you.

559
00:27:40,541 --> 00:27:41,541
Zhan Wang.

560
00:27:42,083 --> 00:27:43,083
Zhan Wang.

561
00:27:45,083 --> 00:27:46,083
Zhan Wang.

562
00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:47,250
Zhan Wang, are you okay?
